        "standfirst":"The dynastic ruler behind Dubai's vertiginous transformation has made his mark in Britain as racing's biggest benefactor. But will a doping scandal at one of his stables cause untold damage to his name?",
        "shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3fefv",
        "thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/4/27/1367063592739/Sheikh-Mohammed-Profile-O-005.jpg",
